&lt;li&gt;Procurement and Contract Management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee bidding and procurement for project design, construction, and long-lead equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage contract signing and execution with suppliers and contractors, ensuring compliance with terms, quality, and deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
