&lt;li&gt;Monitor and stay updated on changes in international trade regulations, customs laws, and import/export compliance requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise internal stakeholders on regulatory changes and operational impacts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure full compliance with customs, trade, and transportation regulations across all import and export activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct periodic compliance reviews and audits, implementing corrective and preventive actions where necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage strategic goods permit applications and ensure compliance for dual-use or controlled products.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
